    "description": "亡灵巫师模拟器回来了。用不同的身体部位拼接亡灵，结合各种神话种族的能力。升级塔楼，并给它一个独特的外观。在这个随机生成的世界中，与成群的敌人作战，抵御巨人的攻击。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277320/extras/fdd7688b6c2701774e6096ad5094f5e7.poster.avif?t=1769752753\" width=616 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277320/extras/fdd7688b6c2701774e6096ad5094f5e7.webm?t=1769752753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超能力亡灵</h2>用各种神话种族的身体部位拼接属于你的亡灵，解锁无数攻击和技能组合。赋予它们飞跃高耸的山脉、淌过湍急的河流和炽热的熔岩，克服重重障碍的超能力。在夜幕的掩护下，你的亡灵更加强大。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277320/extras/3b590706c2a8d28bb718d05f4809e9ce.poster.avif?t=1769752753\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277320/extras/3b590706c2a8d28bb718d05f4809e9ce.webm?t=1769752753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的亡灵法师塔楼</h2>使用各种组件材料升级塔楼，给它一个独特的外观。建设亡灵实验室，培育身体部位和升级魔法科技设备，修炼强大的法术并强化你的亡灵战士。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277320/extras/7b9ea20a3fce22256ba82a83d148d1e2.poster.avif?t=1769752753\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277320/extras/7b9ea20a3fce22256ba82a83d148d1e2.webm?t=1769752753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >完全由随机程序生成世界</h2>在随机生成世界中探索数十个生物群落，并在地图上查看被征服的领土。在创造亡灵时，使用合适的身体部位，征服高山、静寂的沼泽和茂密的森林。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277320/extras/7d92148a13ef9f616aff41ba604a6803.poster.avif?t=1769752753\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277320/extras/7d92148a13ef9f616aff41ba604a6803.webm?t=1769752753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >巨人攻击</h2>这一次，你将不得不面对新的庞大怪物，它们可以轻易摧毁你的塔楼。但你也有机会创造巨人，一举反击。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277320/extras/26a03c3abfd09bedf53ce9b02236b0b4.poster.avif?t=1769752753\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277320/extras/26a03c3abfd09bedf53ce9b02236b0b4.webm?t=1769752753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
